flowchart TD
    A[Apply Leave] --> B[Validate Employee ID]
    B --> C{Dates Valid?}
    C -- No --> X[Reject Request]
    C -- Yes --> D{Balance Enough?}
    D -- No --> X
    D -- Yes --> E[Submit Request]
    E --> F[Admin Review]
    F --> G{Approve?}
    G -- No --> H[Reject + Notify]
    G -- Yes --> I[Approve + Update Balance]
